You need the following libraries:

libfuse >= 2.6  http://fuse.sourceforge.net
libzip >= 0.8   http://www.nih.at/libzip/

Make sure that libfuse are compiled with -D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64!

The following tools are required:

C++ compiler    g++ 4.2.3 or other modern C++ compiler
pkg-config      http://pkg-config.freedesktop.org/
GNU make        http://www.gnu.org/software/make/

To build fuse-zip do the following:

$ make

To install do:

# make install

as root or use sudo.

To uninstall:

# make uninstall

